The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Frontpage | Wedding on Gaga lips
                                                                                                                                                 1                                                                                Wedding on Gaga lips
                          Lady Gaga                    
	London, Oct. 3 (PTI): Pop sensation Lady Gaga may wear unconventional costumes but when it comes to her tying the knot with boyfriend Luc Carl, she wants a traditional ceremony.         
	The Poker Face hitmaker, who created ripples with her meat dress at last months MTV Video Music Awards, has told her friends and family that she wants a lavish Christmas wedding in the British countryside, Sun reported online.         
	Lady Gaga has told everyone she plans to get married. She has said she wants a fairy tale wedding in a castle, said a source close to the singer.         
	The flamboyant star will begin the European leg of her Monster Ball tour in Helsinki on October 13 and plans to finish her work commitments by Christmas.         
	We finish the European leg in London just before Christmas and the timing is perfect for the wedding, the source added.         
	It is believed that the couple want their wedding bands to be like Elvis Presleys horseshoe ring. The 24-year-old singer and Luc began dating in 2005 before she became a star.                                                                                                                                            
